WEBVTT

00:02:58.223 --> 00:03:01.910
shu sabab umri davomida stress bilan 
ko’proq to’qnashishadi.

00:03:01.910 --> 00:03:04.675
Bular epigenetik o’zgarishlardir,

00:03:04.675 --> 00:03:07.524
ya'ni bevosita genetik kodni 
o’zgartirmay turib,

00:03:07.524 --> 00:03:10.514
qaysi genlar ta'sirida irsiylanishiga 
ta'sir ko'rsatadi.

00:03:10.514 --> 00:03:14.361
Onalarning o’rni almashtirilgan taqdirda 
vaziyatga o’zgarish yasash mumkin.

00:03:14.361 --> 00:03:16.123
Hayratlanarli jihat shundaki,

00:03:16.123 --> 00:03:19.788
yakka kalamush onasi tufayli yuz bergan 
epigenetik o’zgarishlar

00:03:19.788 --> 00:03:23.622
undan keyingi kalmushlarning avlodlariga 
uzatilgan.

00:03:23.622 --> 00:03:28.077
Boshqacha aytganda, bu jarayonning 
natijasi nasldan-naslga o’tadi.

00:03:28.077 --> 00:03:30.417
Yaxshi xabar ham yo'q emas.